QuestData.Title: Sins of the Sea Witch
QuestData.Description: That vile worm has earned a thousand deaths!$b$bIt won't be easy. She and her minions are firmly entrenched in this place, but she's bound to be exhausted from her fight with Neptulon.$b$bNow is the time to strike! We won't have another opportunity like this.$b$bRun her through, $n!
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay Lady Naz'jar in the Throne of Tides.
